piratory/coronavirus/novelcoronavirus/casesinireland/epidemiologyofcovid-19inireland/ Epidemiology of COVID-19 in Ireland] published by [[Health Protection Surveillance Centre]]\n\n===Medical journals===\n\n* [https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/pages/coronavirus-alert Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19)] by [[JAMA (journal)|JAMA]]\n* [https://www.bmj.com/coronavirus Coronavirus: News and Resources] by [[BMJ (company)|BMJ Publishing Group]]\n* [https://www.elsevier.com/connect/coronavirus-information-center Novel Coronavirus Information Center] by [[Elsevier]]\n* [https://www.thelancet.com/coronavirus COVID-19 Resource Centre] by [[The Lancet]]\n* [https://www.springernature.com/gp/researchers/campaigns/coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 and COVID-19] by [[Nature (journal)|Nature]]\n* [https://www.nejm.org/coronavirus Coronavirus (Covid-19)] by [[New England Journal of Medicine]]\n* [https://novel-coronavirus.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/ Covid-19: Novel Coronavirus] by [[Wiley (publisher)|Wiley Publishing]]\n\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|short=true}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2019-20 coronavirus pandemic}}\n[[Category:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic| ]]\n[[Category:2010s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in China]]\n[[Category:2019 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2019 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2020 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2020 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:21st-century epidemics]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Atypical pneumonias]]\n[[Category:Current events]]\n[[Category:December 2019 events in China]]\n[[Category:February 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:Health disasters in China]]\n[[Category:History of Wuhan]]\n[[Category:January 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:March 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:Occupational safety and health]]\n[[Category:Pandemics]]\n[[Category:Pandemics with high degree of misinformation]]\n[[Category:Public Health Emergency of International Concern]]\n", "text_old": "{{pp-protected|small=yes}}\n<!--NOTE: Please discuss on talk page before putting a \"current event\" template here. This is intended for short-term use only per advice at Template:Current. When removing content, please also remove its associated references. Thank you.-->\n{{short description|Ongoing pandemic of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)}}\n{{Use British English Oxford spelling|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{bots|deny=RMCD bot}}\n{{Infobox pandemic\n| name            = 2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic\n| map1            = COVID-19 Outbreak World Map per Capita.svg{{!}}upright=1.5\n| legend1         = {{Center|Map of confirmed cases per capita {{as of|2020|4|19|lc=y}}}}\n<div style=\"padding-left:3em; padding-right:0; overflow:hidden;\">\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#840000; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;2,000+ confirmed cases per million</div>\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#cc0c0a; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;500\u20132,000 confirmed cases per million</div>\n<div class=\"legend\" style=\"-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;page-break-inside: avoid;break-inside: avoid-column\"><span class=\"legend-color\" style=\"display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color:#e45353; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;\"