an, China (capital of Hubei province)\" to \"Wuhan, Hubei\". Cities such as LA are commonly written \"Los Angeles, California\" in Wikipedia. (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cinema_of_the_United_States) This is just to standardise and remove unnecessary info.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E2%80%9320_coronavirus_pandemic"}
