th Anniversary Remaster - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - [[Instrumental]]\n| title35     = [[Discipline (instrumental)|Discipline]]\n| writer35    = \n| length35    = \n| note35      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - [[instrumental]]\n| title36     = [[Matte Kudasai]]\n| writer36    = \n| length36    = \n| note36      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - Alternate version\n\n| title37     = Elephant Talk\n| writer37    = \n| length37    = \n| note37      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48)\n| title38     = Frame by Frame\n| writer38    = \n| length38    = \n| note38      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48)\n| title39     = [[Matte Kudasai]]\n| writer39    = \n| length39    = \n| note39      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48) - {{Nihongo2|\u5f85\u3063\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044}}, Please Wait\n| title40     = [[Indiscipline]]\n| writer40    = \n| length40    = \n| note40      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48)\n| title41     = [[Thela Hun Ginjeet]]\n| writer41    = \n| length41    = \n| note41      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48)\n| title42     = The Sheltering Sky\n| writer42    = \n| length42    = \n| note42      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48) - [[Instrumental]]\n| title43     = [[Discipline (instrumental)|Discipline]]\n| writer43    = \n| length43    = \n| note43      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48) - [[instrumental]]\n| title44     = [[Matte Kudasai]]\n| writer44    = \n| length44    = \n| note44      = 30th Anniversary Remaster - PCM Stereo 2.0 (24/48) - Alternate version\n\n| title45     = A selection of Adrian's vocal loops\n| writer45    = \n| length45    = 0:51\n| note45      = Additional Tracks - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96)\n| title46     = The Sheltering Sky\n| writer46    = \n| length46    = 8:27\n| note46      = Additional Tracks - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - Alternate [