um - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround\n| title10     = [[Matte Kudasai]]\n| writer10    = \n| length10    = \n| note10      = Original Album - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround - {{Nihongo2|\u5f85\u3063\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044}}, Please Wait\n| title11     = [[Indiscipline]]\n| writer11    = \n| length11    = \n| note11      = Original Album - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround\n| title12     = [[Thela Hun Ginjeet]]\n| writer12    = \n| length12    = \n| note12      = Original Album - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround\n| title13     = The Sheltering Sky\n| writer13    = \n| length13    = \n| note13      = Original Album - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround - [[Instrumental]]\n| title14     = [[Discipline (instrumental)|Discipline]]\n| writer14    = \n| length14    = \n| note14      = Original Album - DTS 5.1 Digital Surround - [[instrumental]]\n\n| title15     = Elephant Talk\n| writer15    = \n| length15    = \n| note15      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96)\n| title16     = Frame by Frame\n| writer16    = \n| length16    = \n| note16      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96)\n| title17     = [[Matte Kudasai]]\n| writer17    = \n| length17    = \n| note17      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - {{Nihongo2|\u5f85\u3063\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044}}, Please Wait\n| title18     = [[Indiscipline]]\n| writer18    = \n| length18    = \n| note18      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96)\n| title19     = [[Thela Hun Ginjeet]]\n| writer19    = \n| length19    = \n| note19      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96)\n| title20     = The Sheltering Sky\n| writer20    = \n| length20    = \n| note20      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - [[Instrumental]]\n| title21     = [[Discipline (instrumental)|Discipline]]\n| writer21    = \n| length21    = \n| note21      = 2011 Stereo Mix - MLP Lossless Stereo (24/96) - [[instrumental]]\n\n| title22     = Elephant Talk\n| writer22    = \n| length22    = \n| note22      = 2011 Stereo Mix - PCM Stereo 